<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='382740' id='t-382740'>till it looped around the whole ward, and then he said,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='386313' id='t-386313'>&quot;Okay, everybody, hold on to your straws.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='390245' id='t-390245'>And we did. And he said, &quot;Right. Now we're all connected.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='397220' id='t-397220'>And as we held on, and we breathed as one,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='402680' id='t-402680'>we knew we weren't on this journey alone.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='407033' id='t-407033'>And even lying paralyzed in the spinal ward,</span>
