<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='418011' id='t-418011'>that I had never experienced before.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='422355' id='t-422355'>And each of us knew that when we left the spinal ward</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='426836' id='t-426836'>we would never be the same.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:22
