<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='431655' id='t-431655'>After six months, it was time to go home.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='435817' id='t-435817'>I remember Dad pushing me outside in my wheelchair,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='439283' id='t-439283'>wrapped in a plaster body cast,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='442144' id='t-442144'>and feeling the sun on my face for the first time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='445115' id='t-445115'>I soaked it up and I thought,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='447053' id='t-447053'>how could I ever have taken this for granted?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='450927' id='t-450927'>I felt so incredibly grateful for my life.</span>
