<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477972' id='t-477972'>But you're going to get home and realize</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480142' id='t-480142'>how different life is.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
