<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='482238' id='t-482238'>And I got home and something happened.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488641' id='t-488641'>I realized Sister Sam was right.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491660' id='t-491660'>I did get depressed.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494554' id='t-494554'>I was in my wheelchair. I had no feeling from the waist down,</span>
