<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='539537' id='t-539537'>And then I remembered my friends</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543436' id='t-543436'>that were still in the spinal ward,</span>
